#GumHealthDay2022 #treatyourgums #gumhealth #Himalayadentalcare #Himalayagumcare #TreatyourgumwithHimalaya

The Himalaya Ayurveda gum care toothpaste is formulated based on the Ayurvedic practices of oral care. Enriched with 13 herbs, it helps in improving gum health and overall oral health.
Tumburu aids in relieving toothache.
Dadima (Pomegranate) is an effective astringent.
Babbula prevents bleeding gums and strengthens teeth.
Triphala helps relieve tooth decay.
Nirgundi helps in relieving toothache.
Vidanga has antimicrobial properties.
Neem helps fight germs.
Pilu (Miswak) helps reduce dental plaque.
Irimeda improves gum health.
Khadira helps in tightening gums.
Bakula improves gum and teeth health.

#GumHealthDay2020 #treatyourgumswith Himalaya #gumhealth
